&lt;p&gt;As our first GTM Knowledge Engineer, you’ll sit at the intersection of Revenue Enablement, Revenue Operations, and Information Systems within the Go-to-Market Center of Excellence. In this highly impactful role, you’ll build, deploy, and improve the intelligent interfaces, AI agents, and knowledge systems that support our commercial teams and reduce friction across the seller workflow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role carries a dual mandate. First, you’ll create and operationalize GTM agents that automate seller workflows such as meeting prep, POV generation, certification, stakeholder mapping, and ROI modeling. Second, you’ll help reduce systemic friction across the quote-to-cash process by translating complex packaging, policy, and process requirements into clear, proactive user-layer guardrails that help teams move faster and more consistently.&lt;/p&gt;
