&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;We do not believe in the ‘perfect’ candidate. If you’re passionate about the role and feel you can contribute meaningfully, we encourage you to apply. This is a full-time &lt;strong&gt;position based in our Oakland, California office, with a hybrid schedule&lt;/strong&gt;: in-office Monday, Wednesday, and Thursday.&lt;/p&gt;
