&lt;p&gt;Everlaw is evolving its release infrastructure to support a future where AI agents actively participate in deployments. We are looking for a hands-on Senior Software Engineer to build, optimize, and harden the pipelines, data models, and APIs that make this possible.&lt;/p&gt;
